### 2. 팔로우 기능 예상 코드 구조 (스킬 가이드 기준)

프로젝트 아키텍처에 따르면, 팔로우 기능은 다음과 같은 구조를 가져야 합니다:

#### A. **Entity & Repository** (`domain/` 모듈)
```
위치: domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/

entity/user/FollowEntity
- id: String (UUID)
- followerId: String (팔로우하는 사용자)
- followingId: String (팔로우되는 사용자)
- createdAt: LocalDateTime
- updatedAt: LocalDateTime
- Catalog: maum

repository/user/FollowRepository
- findByFollowerId(followerId: String): List<FollowEntity>
- findByFollowingId(followingId: String): List<FollowEntity>
- findByFollowerIdAndFollowingId(followerId: String, followingId: String): Optional<FollowEntity>
```

#### B. **Proto & gRPC Service** (`user/` 모듈 + `protobuf/`)
```
Proto 파일: protobuf/src/main/proto/user/user.proto

service UserService {
  rpc FollowUser(FollowUserRequest) returns (FollowUserResponse);
  rpc UnfollowUser(UnfollowUserRequest) returns (UnfollowUserResponse);
  rpc GetFollowerCount(GetFollowerCountRequest) returns (GetFollowerCountResponse);
  rpc GetFollowingCount(GetFollowingCountRequest) returns (GetFollowingCountResponse);
  rpc CheckFollowStatus(CheckFollowStatusRequest) returns (CheckFollowStatusResponse);
}

message FollowUserRequest {
  string follower_id = 1;
  string following_id = 2;
}

message FollowUserResponse {
  bool success = 1;
}
```

gRPC Service: `user/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/controller/UserGrpcService`
- `followUser(request, observer)` → ServiceLayer 호출
- `unfollowUser(request, observer)` → ServiceLayer 호출
- 예외 처리: `Status.NOT_FOUND`, `Status.INVALID_ARGUMENT`

#### C. **Business Service** (`user/` 모듈)
```
위치: user/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/service/UserService.kt

@Service
class UserService(
    private val followRepository: FollowRepository,
    private val userRepository: UserRepository,
    private val eventPublisher: ApplicationEventPublisher,
) {
    @Transactional
    fun followUser(followerId: String, followingId: String): Boolean {
        // 1. 사용자 존재 확인
        userRepository.findById(followerId).orElseThrow { ... }
        userRepository.findById(followingId).orElseThrow { ... }

        // 2. 중복 팔로우 확인
        if (followRepository.findByFollowerIdAndFollowingId(followerId, followingId).isPresent) {
            throw AlreadyFollowingException()
        }

        // 3. 자기 자신 팔로우 방지
        if (followerId == followingId) {
            throw InvalidFollowException()
        }

        // 4. 저장
        val follow = FollowEntity(followerId = followerId, followingId = followingId)
        followRepository.save(follow)

        // 5. 이벤트 발행
        eventPublisher.publishEvent(UserFollowedEvent(followingId, followerId))
        return true
    }

    @Transactional
    fun unfollowUser(followerId: String, followingId: String): Boolean {
        val follow = followRepository
            .findByFollowerIdAndFollowingId(followerId, followingId)
            .orElseThrow { NotFoundException() }
        followRepository.delete(follow)
        eventPublisher.publishEvent(UserUnfollowedEvent(followingId, followerId))
        return true
    }

    @Transactional(readOnly = true)
    fun getFollowerCount(userId: String): Int {
        return followRepository.findByFollowingId(userId).size
    }

    @Transactional(readOnly = true)
    fun getFollowingCount(userId: String): Int {
        return followRepository.findByFollowerId(userId).size
    }
}
```

#### D. **GraphQL Schema & Controller**
```
GraphQL Schema: graphql/src/main/resources/graphql/follow.graphqls

type User {
    id: ID!
    nickname: String!
    followerCount: Int!
    followingCount: Int!
}

extend type Query {
    checkFollowStatus(targetUserId: ID!): Boolean!
}

extend type Mutation {
    followUser(targetUserId: ID!): Boolean!
    unfollowUser(targetUserId: ID!): Boolean!
}

GraphQL Controller: graphql/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/controller/user/UserController.kt

@Controller
class UserController(
    private val userService: UserService,
) {
    @MutationMapping
    @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
    fun followUser(
        @UserId userId: String,
        @Argument targetUserId: String,
    ): Boolean {
        return userService.followUser(userId, targetUserId)
    }

    @MutationMapping
    @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
    fun unfollowUser(
        @UserId userId: String,
        @Argument targetUserId: String,
    ): Boolean {
        return userService.unfollowUser(userId, targetUserId)
    }
}
```

#### E. **Test 파일 구조**
```
user/src/test/kotlin/com/maum/backend/service/UserServiceTest.kt
- should follow user successfully
- should throw when user not found
- should throw when already following
- should throw when following self
- should unfollow user successfully
- should return follower count
- should return following count

user/src/test/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/FollowRepositoryTest.kt
- should find by follower_id
- should find by following_id
- should find by follower_id and following_id
- should not find non-existent follow
```

### 3. 예외 처리 로직
```
- NotFoundException: 사용자가 존재하지 않을 때
- AlreadyFollowingException: 이미 팔로우하고 있을 때
- InvalidFollowException: 자기 자신을 팔로우하려고 할 때
- StatusRuntimeException: gRPC 통신 에러
```

### 4. 의존성 관계도
```
GraphQL Controller
    ↓
GraphQL Service (gRPC Client)
    ↓
gRPC Service (user 모듈의 controller)
    ↓
UserService (business logic)
    ↓
FollowRepository, UserRepository (JPA)
    ↓
FollowEntity, UserEntity (JPA)
```

